title: Braun Intertec acquires Apex Geoscience

Home / Brief / Braun Intertec acquires Apex Geoscience Braun Intertec acquires Apex Geoscience By: Brian Johnson October 2, 2015 12:37 pm 0 Bloomington-based Braun Intertec has acquired Apex Geoscience, a Tyler, Texas-based provider of engineering, testing and environmental consulting services. The acquisition, which became effective Sept. 25, increases the Braun Intertecâ€™s presence in Texas and expands the company into Louisiana and Oklahoma, the company said in a press release.
